{"tid":1015873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[蝗蠙鬥]不滿被阻進地鐵站　支那女菲律賓發難向警潑豆腐花被捕","createTime":"2019-02-10T11:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T08:23:52.000Z","uid":23162,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0d9fc3682c72a31ba68b0f2a5296a8cdbe35184f","tid":1015873,"uid":23162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T11:43:56.000Z","msg":"菲律賓馬尼拉一名支那裔女子周六（9日）帶着豆腐花，嘗試進地鐵站乘搭列車時，被保安人員截停。她在一怒之下，竟將手中的豆腐花潑向趕到現場的警員，最終遭警方拘捕；她事後向警方道歉，現已獲釋。 <br />\n<br />\n當地的媒體報道，該名23歲譯音姓張的女子在進入車站時，被要求先將豆腐花吃掉。然而，該名女子拒絕，當另一名警員到場解釋後，她更將豆腐花直接倒向對方身上。由網民提供的照片見到，警員的胸口、雙手有一大片奶白色物體，相信是女子的豆腐花。 <br />\n<br />\n鐵路營運公司於周五（8日）表示，因為上月曾接獲炸彈威脅，近日決定禁止乘客在站內和列車上攜帶任何液體。惟新措施遭不少乘客批評。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V6p7CgB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV6p7CgB.png&h=535a442a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fJzLoWC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfJzLoWC.png&h=580cdb25&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nmAVL9Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnmAVL9Z.png&h=df854e1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190209/mobile/bkn-20190209190719715-0209_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190209%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190209190719715-0209_00952_001.html&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BEn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=ebbf4de4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190209/mobile/bkn-20190209190719715-0209_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c69ff308804172d748ac53b9edb77f3837eaac15","tid":1015873,"uid":14103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T11:46:49.000Z","msg":"唔打一鑊先？！"},{"pid":"4958823444aadcfcdc08ee4378b9f5cb620e99b5","tid":1015873,"uid":34223,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T11:51:32.000Z","msg":"下等人vs下等國家"},{"pid":"7ee45a